parameters: "Let's go to the Monster Fight Arena!"
"Just one step away from city-wide domination!\nWho is the strongest monster...? Stay tuned!"

Memimi: Hmm, it looks like you've cleaned properly... Even
though you were the boss of a major organization until
recently, now you're just one of the lowest-ranking members.
Don't expect any special treatment.

Anomalocaris: Hmph... Having been defeated in the Monster
Fight, I have no choice but to work diligently as a
subordinate... It's not such a bad feeling...

Cerberus Octopus: I thought I might be subjected to some
underhanded bullying, but to be treated just like any other
member without any punishment... Aren't you being too
kind...? After all, I was originally an enemy...

Memimi: Kukuku, do I look like such a petty monster to you?
Don't worry about it... What I expect from you all is
contribution to the organization and loyalty to the great
leader Shark Broccoli-sama!

Shark Broccoli: Hmm... As expected of Shark Duke... Truly a
model monster! A fitting behavior for the next leader.

Memimi: Haha! Great Leader-sama!! I am utterly delighted!!
Thank you for your hard work in the meeting with the Monster
Fight management headquarters!!

Shark Broccoli: Ah, the schedule for the next match has
finally been decided... Tonight, there will be a face-to-
face meeting with the opposing organization, so you will
accompany me... It will likely be a battle with the biggest
and strongest opponent we've faced so far...

Cerberus Octopus: So, it's finally happening... The Monster
Fight with the last of the four major organizations in the
city...! At last, with that legendary monster... Ohhh...!

Anomalocaris: The winner will become the largest force in
the city... In other words, they will have the right to
unify all organizations in the city and end the warring
states period of the underworld!! But... if the opponent is
that monster... Even for Shark Duke...

Shark Duke: Silence! You lowly minions!!! There's no way I
will lose... I will deliver victory to Shark Broccoli Great
Leader-sama! Even if the opponent is "Dynamite Abalone," the
strongest monster known as "The Powder Keg with Plenty of
Juice"!

Just mentioning it causes such trembling, a legendary
strongest monster. Yet Memimi, in order to fulfill her own
strength and loyalty to Shark Broccoli, steeled herself...

Memimi: Alright, maybe I'll relax and pass the time until
tonight... I'm not scared, but I can't be too optimistic
either. I need to sharpen my mind while not getting too
tense...
